# Google Drive API key used by the "Carrusel de Imágenes (Drive)" block.
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com/ and create (or select) a project.
# 2. Enable the "Google Drive API" for that project.
# 3. Create an API Key under "Credentials" and restrict it by HTTP referrer
#    (your domain / localhost) since this key is exposed to the browser.
# 4. Share the target Drive folder as "Anyone with the link" (Viewer).
PUBLIC_GOOGLE_DRIVE_API_KEY=
